# STORM Specification Index

## Purpose
Master index for all STORM (Self-Organizing Regenerative Task Management) specifications.

## Architecture
STORM is NOT a separate binary. It is a **subcommand system** of `tri` CLI:
```bash
tri storm run        # Execute STORM operation
tri storm status     # Show checkpoint status
tri storm resume     # Continue from checkpoint
tri storm init       # Initialize STORM structure
```

## Specifications List

| Spec | Module | Description | Status |
|------|--------|-------------|--------|
| [tri_storm_integration.tri](../tri_storm_integration.tri) | tri.storm | Main storm integration into tri CLI | ✅ |
| [storm_main.tri](./storm_main.tri) | tri.storm | Storm subcommand handler | ✅ |
| [golden_chain.tri](./golden_chain.tri) | storm.golden_chain | 28-link pipeline with neuro mapping | ✅ |
| [config.tri](./config.tri) | storm.config | Configuration parser | ✅ |
| [phoenix_bridge.tri](./phoenix_bridge.tri) | storm.phoenix_bridge | Self-healing cell system | ✅ |

