## P1 Ethical Infrastructure
These are Phase 1 priority implementations (corruption/fairness/toxicity):

1. **OFC (Палата ценностей)** — Toxic verdict
   - Spec: [brain_ofc.tri](./brain_ofc.tri)
   - 12D ethical metric system
   - CLI: `tri ofc verdict --toxic`

2. **HABENULA (Антикоррупционный датчик)** — Unfair reward detection
   - Spec: [brain_habenula.tri](./brain_habenula.tri)
   - reward/effort ratio analysis
   - CLI: `tri habenula unfair_detect`

3. **AMYGDALA (Страж ошибок)** — MNL pattern
   - Spec: [brain_amygdala.tri](./brain_amygdala.tri)
   - 3x failed = auto-blacklist
   - CLI: `tri amygdala check_fear`

## File Structure (After Integration)
```
specs/storm/
├── INDEX.tri                    # This file
├── tri_storm_integration.tri       # Main tri.storm integration
├── tri_brain_zones_integration.tri # Unified brain zone handler
├── storm_main.tri               # Storm subcommand (src/tri/storm.zig)
├── golden_chain.tri             # 28-link pipeline (src/storm/golden_chain.zig)
├── config.tri                   # Configuration (src/storm/config.zig)
├── phoenix_bridge.tri            # Self-healing (src/storm/phoenix_bridge.zig)
├── experience_engine.tri          # MNL pattern (src/storm/experience_engine.zig)
├── brain_ofc.tri               # OFC - toxic verdict (src/storm/brain_zones/ofc.zig)
├── brain_habenula.tri           # Habenula - anti-corruption (src/storm/brain_zones/habenula.zig)
└── brain_amygdala.tri           # Amygdala - blacklist (src/storm/brain_zones/amygdala.zig)
```

