## Next Steps (VIBEE Codegen)
Now that .tri specs are complete, run VIBEE to generate .zig implementations:

```bash
# Generate storm integration
zig build vibee --gen specs/tri_storm_integration.tri

# Generate brain zones integration
zig build vibee --gen specs/tri_brain_zones_integration.tri

# Generate storm subcommand handler
zig build vibee --gen specs/storm_main.tri
```

## CLI Examples (After Implementation)
```bash
# STORM operations
tri storm run --waves=5 --agents=32
tri storm status --wave=2
tri storm resume --checkpoint=link-15
tri storm init

# Brain zone operations
tri ofc verdict --toxic "deploy without review"
tri habenula unfair_detect
tri amygdala check_fear "flaky test"
```
